title: Blue Jays beat Rangers 6-3 to win wild Game 5
text: > Sports Blue Jays beat Rangers 6-3 to win wild Game 5 The Toronto Blue Jays celebrate after winning Game 5 of baseball's American League Division Series against the Texas Rangers, Wednesday, Oct. 14, 2015, in Toronto. The Blue Jays clinched their first trip to the American League Championship Series since 1993, overcoming one of the most bizarre plays in playoff history by taking advantage of three Rangers errors for a 6-3 victory. (Darren Calabrese/The Canadian Press via AP) MANDATORY CREDIT
